short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension is used for browser interaction with Swisscom DIM/BIM.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is the latest production version of the "Swisscom DIM" extension.

This extension is used to remote control your browser from Swisscom DIM/BIM.
It requires Gensys WDE and a locally installed DIM.
